            <div class="relative py-32 px-6 sm:py-40 lg:py-56 lg:px-8 lg:pr-0">
              <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-xl">
                <div class="hidden sm:mt-10 sm:flex">
                  <p class="relative py-1 px-3 text-sm leading-6 text-red-700">
                    Somos caipiras e gostamos de tecnologia!
